GET IN TOUCH

Vendors/Publishers

Have a comic book or other pop-culture product you want to sell through Diamond? Review our Submissions Guidelines for more information, then contact our Submissions Team.

Currently a Diamond Vendor / Publisher? Log into our Vendor Services Website to access your account.

Retailers/Customers

Interested in becoming a Diamond Retail Customer or opening your own comic book shop? Learn more on our Retailer Website or contact our New Accounts Team.

Currently a Diamond Retail Customer? Log into our Retailer Services Website to access your account as well as the latest news and product info.

Marketing

For marketing, advertising, and promotional partnerships, contact our Marketing Team.

Press

Contact our Media Relations Team or view our Press & Media Portal for more information.
